items.sentence: Tom tried to do something new every day for 30 days.

Tom told us that he'd be willing to teach us French.
Tom snuck into the kitchen and got something to eat.

I wonder whether Tom knows where Mary's umbrella is.

Tom chose the big one, and Mary chose the small one.
Tom is grandfathered in with an unlimited data plan.
Godfathers and godmothers don't need to be a couple.
